---
import Countdown from "../Countdown/countdown.astro";
import "../../styles/global.css";
import Bgopt from "../../../image/bgopt.jpg"
---
<div class="flex flex-col">
<section class="section-one relative flex h-[100vh] w-full safe-area-padding z-10 border border-white">
    <div class="backgroundimagehero bg-cover bg-center w-full mask-fade-bottom absolute inset-0"></div>

    <div class="landing-wrapper relative flex flex-col  border border-white items-center p-4 md:p-20 w-full">
        <div id="landing" class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center w-full border ">
            <div id="hovereffect" class="relative flex flex-col items-center transition-all duration-700 ease-in-out overflow-hidden py-10 md:py-20 animate-lapieza px-4 md:px-40 align-center">
                <div class="absolute bottom-4 md:bottom-10 text-white  opacity-0 translate-y-10 animate-text-appear z-1 text-center justify-center animate-fade-in animate-scale animate-flip-in-y">
                    <p class="text-base md:text-xl font-Lexend">La</p>
                    <p class="font-Rubik text-5xl md:text-8xl">Pieza</p>
                    <p class="font-Lexend text-sm md:text-base">Adrià Solà Pastor</p>
                    <p class="text-sm md:text-base">14 DE <span class="font-Lexend text-xl md:text-2xl">MAYO</span></p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="w-[300px] h-[300px] md:w-[600px]  md:h-[600px] flex items-center justify-center animate-holy-glow">
                    <div class="lapiezaimg relative w-[250px]   h-[250px] md:w-[500px] md:h-[500px] mt-4 md:mt-10 animate-logo-move animate-slide-in-bottom"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-end p-2 md:p-8 border border-red-600"></div> -->
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-img relative  flex flex-col items-center gap-4 px-3 py-6 w-full">
    <div class="event-img w-full max-w-[700px] aspect-video rounded-tr-lg rounded-bl-lg bg-gray-200"></div>
    
    <button class="font-Lexend text-white text-sm md:text-base border border-blue-400 px-4 py-2 md:px-5 md:py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-blue-500/10 hover:backdrop-blur-md hover:shadow-[0_0_15px_3px_rgba(100,200,255,0.5)] active:scale-95">
        Registrate <strong>AHORA</strong>
    </button>
</section>

<section class="flex justify-center px-4 md:px-10 mt-6 md:mt-10 py-6 md:py-10 text-center">
    <Countdown />
</section>

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6 md:mb-10 font-Lexend text-white">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
        <details class="group border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-3 md:p-4 transition-all duration-300 font-lexend">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg font-medium font-Lexend text-white">
                <span>El evento es gratis?</span>
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-neutral-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 md:mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Si, Puedes Unirte al evento sin ningun tipo de pago de por medio. Es un evento gratuito para todo el mundo.
            </p>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ Items 2 & 3 similarly adjusted -->
         <details class="group border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-3 md:p-4 transition-all duration-300 font-lexend">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg font-medium font-Lexend text-white">
                <span>Necesito ser mayor de edad?</span>
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-neutral-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 md:mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Como es un evento gratuito , No es necesario que tengas mas de 18 años para poder asistir. Sin embargo a veces hay sorteos a los que solo una persona mayor puede acceder.
            </p>
        </details>
        <details class="group border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-3 md:p-4 transition-all duration-300 font-lexend">
            <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer text-base md:text-lg font-medium font-Lexend text-white">
                <span>Cuando Será el Próximo evento?</span>
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 md:w-5 md:h-5 text-neutral-500 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                </svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-2 md:mt-3 text-sm md:text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
                Aun no se a publicado, Estaos al tanto de las redes sociales , Nos encantaria tenerte como miembro en nuestro proximo evento.
            </p>
        </details>
    </div>
</section>
</div>

<style>
    /* *{border:1px solid red} */
    /* Mobile-first animations */
    @keyframes logoMove {
        0% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
        100% { transform: translateY(50px) scale(1.05); }
    }

    @keyframes textAppear {
        0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
        60% { opacity: 0; }
        100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-150px); }
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        @keyframes logoMove {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
            100% { transform: translateY(100px) scale(1.1); }
        }

        @keyframes textAppear {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            60% { opacity: 0; }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(-350px); }
        }
    }

    @keyframes lapiezaEffect {
        0% { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
        100% { background-color: rgba(7,33,55,0.3); }
    }

    @keyframes holyGlow {
        0%, 100% { 
            opacity: 0.3;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.1),
                        0 0 10px 2px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        50% { 
            opacity: 0.6;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.2),
                        0 0 20px 5px rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
    }

    /* Animation classes */
    .animate-logo-move {
        animation: logoMove 1200ms ease-in-out 500ms forwards;
    }

    .animate-text-appear {
        animation: textAppear 700ms ease-in-out 700ms forwards;
    }

    .animate-lapieza {
        animation: lapiezaEffect 600ms ease-in-out forwards;
    }

    #hovereffect {
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        #hovereffect {
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }

    }
    @media (max-width: 768px){
        .landing-wrapper{
            height:450px;
            margin:0;
            padding:0;
        }
        .section-one{
            height:500px;
        }
    }

    .animate-holy-glow {
        animation: holyGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    /* Safe area padding for notched devices */
    .safe-area-padding {
        padding-left: max(1rem, env(safe-area-inset-left));
        padding-right: max(1rem, env(safe-area-inset-right));
        padding-top: max(1rem, env(safe-area-inset-top));
        padding-bottom: max(1rem, env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
    }

    /* Dynamic viewport height for iOS */
    .min-h-[100dvh] {
        min-height: 100vh;
        min-height: 100dvh;
    }

    /* Tap target sizing for mobile */
    button, [role="button"], summary {
        min-height: 44px;
        min-width: 44px;
    }
</style>